{
 "name": "RPlog_Karrde_and_Joir",
 "title": "Karrde and Joir",
 "summary": "When the smuggler chief Talon Karrde, acting Baron-Administrator of Cloud City, lands the Wild Karrde, he is met on the platform by the cold Bureau of Operations man Count Tsaran Joir, while the nosy Rodian Leebo tries to eavesdrop. The two coolly take each other measure and retire to the Baron-Administrator office for a guarded, fencing conversation about Cloud City production, Joir Imperial Ministry of Commerce background, and the subtle world of threat and insinuation he now inhabits. Beneath the polite business talk, Joir probes Karrde with veiled pressure and an implicit offer, while Karrde -- equally controlled -- deflects with sardonic modesty and frames everything as business. The careful sparring ends with mutual cold courtesies as each takes the measure of the other for future dealings.",
